{"tid":276234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭智左眼骨折　隨時變盲","createTime":"2017-06-08T16:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T06:16:37.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1157,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f65f6536b1ab78f12b853b3a7ee7d63a8a5904c8","tid":276234,"uid":5195,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"中國國家隊隊長鄭智眼部骨折，隨時變盲！下周國足對敍利亞進行世界盃亞洲區外圍賽，但鄭智沒有隨隊備戰，國內傳媒爆料，原來鄭智左眼受傷，如強行操練，最嚴重會失明。<br />\n<br />\n原來，於同菲律賓比賽前一日訓練中，鄭智左眼意外被隊友撞傷，眼部還出現了骨折。當時鄭智感覺到只要眼球轉動，頭部都會極度疼痛。鄭智立刻喺隊醫陪同下連夜前往醫院進行檢查。經過檢查顯示，鄭智的左眼出現骨折，而且眼睛裡有非常一塊細微嘅小塊骨頭，呢個亦係鄭智只要一轉動眼珠就會非常疼痛的原因。<br />\n<br />\n醫生要求鄭智必須要靜養，至少3至5天時間，呢幾日絕對不能進行訓練，防止再意外受傷，這塊小骨頭甚至可能會導致左眼失明。"},{"pid":"e7c4d6e7e7e9e26d00197c34349dce833219a63a","tid":276234,"uid":61105,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc7750ba5bb52e5467c1a95bc5b2acc41da1a91","tid":276234,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分別係有心做低佢搏上位啦"},{"pid":"87b63848bbbc11ffd57eaad3d81bb0d37219c56f","tid":276234,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來依個世界有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07192add03962795df7061d5462948b738a8e48a","tid":276234,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豬隊友<img 